{"tid":928052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【勇武勝利】法國總理宣布半年內不提高燃油稅 冀平息國內亂局","createTime":"2018-12-04T14:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T14:02:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"822d187bbeb678b3e308cee04ef6db983d8cad5a","tid":928052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5c067459e603831a3848956d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5c067459e603831a3848956d&d=PVI6hBKaofi%2BzSQIbQ7rMDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=24394df8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5c067459e603831a3848956d</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://217.218.67.233//photo/20181202/cf3dad10-83c0-4069-9bf1-fe5b71820e0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F217.218.67.233%2F%2Fphoto%2F20181202%2Fcf3dad10-83c0-4069-9bf1-fe5b71820e0e.jpg&h=edd56a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國總理菲利普宣布，六個月內不會提高燃油稅，期望平息國內亂局。<br />\n<br />\n菲利普在國會會晤執政黨議員後，當地周二中午發表全國電視講話，決定暫時擱置提高燃油稅，為期六個月，他稱不希望相關政策損害國家團結。<br />\n<br />\n法國各地連續三個周末爆發「黃背心」反政府示威，上月至今釀成至少3死130傷，400人被捕，其中在巴黎的衝突最為嚴重，內政部形容是半世紀以來最嚴重騷亂。示威者原先要求擱置提高燃油稅，之後加入其他訴求。"},{"pid":"6ab4f269c9bedf654e4e137998bbea90131fa896","tid":928052,"uid":51701,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"lihk 仔好擔心啲文物同工人返唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fe60b6d302d4d67fb62f78bcec3ff0cc983ec5","tid":928052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab4f269c9bedf654e4e137998bbea90131fa896","tid":928052,"uid":51701,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"lihk 仔好擔心啲文物同工人返唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"好彩今年無打算去巴黎玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eda5d565695a68d7b766dee91c759b025a87e3d","tid":92805